column.name: Query
column.value: " update Cadastro.dbo.SYS_DET_CLIENTES set Envio_data_stewardship = GETDATE() where SYS_ID in ( SELECT SYS_ID FROM Cadastro.dbo.SYS_DET_CLIENTES where (valuedocs is null or ltrim(rtrim(valuedocs)) = ' ') and tipo = 'Particular' and estado = 'Activo' and (name is null or ltrim(rtrim(name)) = ' ' or name like '%mass%' or name like '%viva%' or name like '%default%' or name like '%unitel%' or name like '%turista%' or name like '%fixo%' or name like '%nao tem%' or name like '%port in%' or name like '%sem nome%' or name like '%xxx%' or name like '%mas mas%' or name like '%emigrante%' or name like '%test%' or name like '%corporate%' or name like '%obilid%') and name not in ('Massane Biaye', 'Massimo Bove', 'Massimo Olivero', 'Massimo Spinola','Massira Ivone Carvalho Monteiro', 'El Massoudi') AND id_obj = '34928' ) "
